quran[6{c,v,t}:
3,195,"jawab mein un ke rab ne farmaya,"" mein tum mein se kisi ka amal zaya karne wala nahi hon khuwa mard ho ya aurat, tum sab aik dosray ke hum jins ho lehaza jin logon ne meri khatir apne watan chhorey aur jo Meer y raah mein apne gharon se nikalay gay aur sataye gay aur mere liye larray aur maaray gay unn ke sab qasoor mein maaf kar dun ga aur inhen aisay baghoon mein daakhil karoon ga jin ke neechay nhrin behti hon gi yeh unn ki jaza hai Allah ke haan aur behtareen jaza Allah hi ke paas hai """
3,196,ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! duniya ke mulkon mein khuda ke nafarman logon kichallat phirat tumhe kisi dhokay mein nah daaley
3,197,"yeh mehez chand roza zindagi ka thora sa lutaf hai, phir yeh sab jahannum mein jayen ge jo bad tareen jaye qarar hai"
3,198,"bar aks is ke jo log apne rab se drtay hue zindagi busr karte hain un ke liye aisay baagh hain jin ke neechay nhrin behti hain, un baghoon mein woh hamesha rahen ge, Allah ki taraf se yeh samaan ziyafat hai un ke liye, aur jo kuch Allah ke paas hai naik logon ke liye wohi sab se behtar hai"
3,199,"ahal kitaab mein bhi kuch log aisay hain jo Allah ko mantay hain, is kitaab par imaan laatay hain jo tumhari taraf bhaije gayi hai aur iss kitaab prbhi imaan rakhtay hain jo is se pehlay khud un ki taraf bhaije gayi thi, Allah ke agay jhuke hue hain, aur Allah ki ayaat ko thori si qeemat par beech nahi dete un ka ajar un ke rab ke paas hai aur Allah hisaab chukane mein der nahi lagaata"
3,200,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, sabr se kaam lau, baatil paraston ke muqaabla mein pa mardi dikhao, haq ki khidmat ke liye kamar basta raho, aur Allah se drtay raho, umeed hai ke Falah pao ge"
